  {
    "hotel_id": "626205",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/seoul-city-hotel/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "Seoul City Hotel",
    "detail": "We've stayed her for 6 days and it was a memorable experience exploring Korea while staying at Seoul City Hotel. We are very pleased with our hotel because Mrs. Kim the manager was very accommodating. She always makes sure that all are set before we head out for our tour. It is also a major plus that she speaks fluently in English and a little bit of German. She took good care of our mother while we (youngsters) were out to explore the country. She even assisted us at the nearest grocery store because we want to do some grocery shopping before we head home. Breakfast is nothing but perfect because they have salad and almost anything that you’ll want for breakfast. Mrs. Kim even helped us with our laundry and allowed us to have a lunch at the dining hall. I have nothing but good things to say about this hotel and about the staff. I like Omma the one who cleans and provide new linens and toiletries; although she can't speak English she was really nice and she always smiles at us. The place is ideally located at the subway; nearest station just outside the alley is Hyoeyoen Station. Also, the place is just minutes walk to the Make-up heaven of Korea which is Myeong-Dong and also minutes walk going to affordable market which is the Namdaemun. We are looking forward to staying at this Hotel again for our upcoming Korea trip.",
